>> Container model:
	Properties:
		- count
		- size
		- capacity
		- min_capacity






DEFINITIONS

count
	Number of elements currently in container

size
	Number of bytes currently in use (ie. count * element_size_in_bytes)

capacity
	Number of bytes allocated for use by the container. (capacity >= size)

min_capacity
	Minimum number of bytes to be held available for use by the container.
